headline: GTCR nears deal to buy OSTTRA for about $3.2 billion, Bloomberg News reports
summary: Private equity firm GTCR is nearing a deal to buy OSTTRA for about $3.2 billion, Bloomberg News reported on Saturday citing people familiar with the matter. The deal could be announced...
